	/healing-drum-workshop/\n\nDrums are provided. All ages. No experience nec
	essary.\n\nThe Hawk Foundation for Research and Education in African Cultu
	re brings master drummers t o LANGSTON to engage in a well-researched peda
	gogy of community healing through African drumming.\n\nThe Hawk Foundation
	 is a Washington-based drum and education organization that utilizes West 
	African and African American music to promote education\, team bonding\, o
	rganizational de velopment\, and research-based therapy. Through history\,
